results.name: Decimal expansion of a constant related to A255358.
formula: Equals (2*Pi)^(3/4) * exp(-11/240 - 3*Zeta'(-3)) * Product_{n>=1} ((n^3)!/stirling(n^3)), where stirling(n^3) = sqrt(2*Pi) * n^(3*n^3 + 3/2) / exp(n^3) is the Stirling approximation of (n^3)! and Zeta'(-3) = A259068. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Apr 20 2016
results.author: _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Feb 24 2015
